summary:
Awesome! Brie Larson and John Cho Will Receive Honorary Awards at the 2nd Annual LAOFCS Awards Ceremony

As a proud member of...
caption:
Awesome! Brie Larson and John Cho Will Receive Honorary Awards at the 2nd Annual LAOFCS Awards Ceremony

As a proud member of the Los Angeles Online Film Critics Society, I’m super stoked to share you this info announcing that #CaptainMarvel star, Oscar winner #BrieLarson and #Searching star, #JohnCho will receive the honorary awards at the 2nd Annual LAOFCS Awards Ceremony which will take place on Wednesday, January 9, 2019 at the Taglyan Complex in Los Angeles.

summary: BRIE LARSON, BORED LOOPTY-LOO HOUSEWIFE AS SUPERHERO? “I can move planet...  If Captain Marvel can now defeat Thanos without any...
caption:
BRIE LARSON, BORED LOOPTY-LOO HOUSEWIFE AS SUPERHERO? “I can move planet…

If Captain Marvel can now defeat Thanos without any effort… is there any point to the Marvel movies at all?

I think it’s funny that they arranged Brie’s face in the imitation of a human smile for the photo shoot. I can only imagine a lot of wires had to be put in place.
